* This program decode a MPEG-2 video bitstream
* 
* Bitstream filename (string) * test.mpg
* Transport bitstream? (int) * 0
* Video syntax verbose level (0:OFF 1:SEQ 2:GOP 3:PIC 4:SLC 5:MB 6:ALL) (int) * 0
* Video syntax output file (string) * video.syn
* First frame number (int) * 0
* Decode bitstream? (int) * 1
* [Decode?] Output sequence name (string) * 
* [Decode?] Show output video? (int) * 0
* 
* Distortion calculation:
* [Decode?] Compute MSE? (int) * 0
* [MSE?] Original sequence name (string) @ 
* 
* Debugging parameters:
* Frame number (int) * -1
* Macroblock number (int) * -1
* No. of bytes to skip (int) * 0
